                "id": 4,
                "name": "B\u1EA3o v\u1EC7 24/7",
                "description": "H\u1EC7 th\u1ED1ng b\u1EA3o v\u1EC7 chuy\xEAn nghi\u1EC7p 24/7 v\u1EDBi camera gi\xE1m s\xE1t to\xE0n b\u1ED9 t\xF2a nh\xE0. B\u1EA3o v\u1EC7 t\xFAc tr\u1EF1c t\u1EA1i c\u1ED5ng, thang m\xE1y, khu v\u1EF1c chung. \u0110\u1EA3m b\u1EA3o an ninh v\xE0 an to\xE0n cho kh\xE1ch h\xE0ng.",
